  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Besides what they did was that each locomotive had a few-- a few empty cars-- they were not empty in the front of the locomotive-- that were loaded with stone, just heavy, in order when they would go through and this would blow up, it would only hurt the empty-- the empty [INAUDIBLE] and it would not destroy the material.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the idea was that they will put in some 10,000 of those Hungarian/Jewish labor units, and they would cut the entire forest down to the ground.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That would solve their problem with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when it was warm, you know, we didn't get shoes or clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had what we had and it had to last.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was a terrible place to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it was cold and it was frozen, it wasn't so bad, but when it got a little bit warmer, you know, when it got in January, February, it got a little bit warmer, you were in-- in the-- in the mud all the time.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to drag these lumbers and load it on trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was good lumber there, pine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we weren't able to-- we were-- they put us in in barns, and we weren't able to dry out our clothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And many of the-- many of the boys were just getting flu, typhus, and they were falling like flies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Fortunately, this lasted two or three months, and I managed to get through those two, three months more or less.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a [INAUDIBLE], a pair of good shoes, and we were able to talk to the local people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By the way, the local population there, the White Russians, they were-- they were-- they kept the [? subbotnik ?] religion.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
